        <mxCell id="400" value="&lt;b&gt;Skills 3-Tier Degradation&lt;/b&gt;:  Tier 1 Full (name+desc+path) &amp;rarr;&lt;i&gt; if &amp;gt;18K &lt;/i&gt;&amp;rarr; Tier 2 Compact (name+path) &amp;rarr;&lt;i&gt; if still &amp;gt;18K &lt;/i&gt;&amp;rarr; Tier 3 Binary search truncation (&quot;included X of Y&quot;)  |  Skills are LAZY: catalog only, agent reads SKILL.md on demand  |  🆕 v1.2: Skills 实测 30 top + 71 bundled = 101 total" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#6c8ebf;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="490" width="1500" height="35" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
