        <mxCell id="500" value="&lt;b&gt;Hook Infrastructure&lt;/b&gt;:  Priority sorting (higher first)  |  Timeout control per hook  |  Failure policy: fail-open (default, catchErrors=true) / fail-closed  |  Plugin ownership tracking" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFF9C4;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=10;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="30" y="250" width="1490" height="30" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
